      <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;функциональные-колодцы-и-проблемы-ими-вызыванные&#34;&gt;Функциональные колодцы и проблемы ими вызыванные&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#%d1%84%d1%83%d0%bd%d0%ba%d1%86%d0%b8%d0%be%d0%bd%d0%b0%d0%bb%d1%8c%d0%bd%d1%8b%d0%b5-%d0%ba%d0%be%d0%bb%d0%be%d0%b4%d1%86%d1%8b-%d0%b8-%d0%bf%d1%80%d0%be%d0%b1%d0%bb%d0%b5%d0%bc%d1%8b-%d0%b8%d0%bc%d0%b8-%d0%b2%d1%8b%d0%b7%d1%8b%d0%b2%d0%b0%d0%bd%d0%bd%d1%8b%d0%b5&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://tech-notizen-inno.github.io/_images/2024-03-23_13-07-38.png&#34; alt=&#34;&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;три-пути-devops&#34;&gt;Три пути DevOps&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#%d1%82%d1%80%d0%b8-%d0%bf%d1%83%d1%82%d0%b8-devops&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://tech-notizen-inno.github.io/_images/2024-03-15_04-54-41.png&#34; alt=&#34;&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;пять-идеалов-devops&#34;&gt;Пять идеалов DevOps&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#%d0%bf%d1%8f%d1%82%d1%8c-%d0%b8%d0%b4%d0%b5%d0%b0%d0%bb%d0%be%d0%b2-devops&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://tech-notizen-inno.github.io/_images/2024-03-15_05-05-19.png&#34; alt=&#34;&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;img src=&#34;https://tech-notizen-inno.github.io/_images/2024-03-15_05-05-27.png&#34; alt=&#34;&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;как-поступать-в-сложной-ситуации&#34;&gt;Как поступать в сложной ситуации&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#%d0%ba%d0%b0%d0%ba-%d0%bf%d0%be%d1%81%d1%82%d1%83%d0%bf%d0%b0%d1%82%d1%8c-%d0%b2-%d1%81%d0%bb%d0%be%d0%b6%d0%bd%d0%be%d0%b9-%d1%81%d0%b8%d1%82%d1%83%d0%b0%d1%86%d0%b8%d0%b8&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://tech-notizen-inno.github.io/_images/2024-03-15_05-14-49.png&#34; alt=&#34;&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;подход-к-ошибкам&#34;&gt;Подход к ошибкам&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#%d0%bf%d0%be%d0%b4%d1%85%d0%be%d0%b4-%d0%ba-%d0%be%d1%88%