      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://tech-notizen-inno.github.io/_images/S_20250109-084100.png&#34; alt=&#34;&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;img src=&#34;https://tech-notizen-inno.github.io/_images/S_20250109-084914.png&#34; alt=&#34;&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;img src=&#34;https://tech-notizen-inno.github.io/_images/S_20250109-085006.png&#34; alt=&#34;&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;img src=&#34;https://tech-notizen-inno.github.io/_images/S_20250109-085321.png&#34; alt=&#34;&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;img src=&#34;https://tech-notizen-inno.github.io/_images/S_20250109-155127.png&#34; alt=&#34;&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
